Project Documentation

Project Name: Microservices CI Implementation using Azure DevOps

Project Overview (What I Built)

This project demonstrates a containerized microservices architecture integrated with a CI pipeline.

The system includes:

Frontend service (Nginx container)

Backend API (Node.js + Express)

MongoDB database container

Docker-based containerization

CI pipeline implemented in Azure DevOps

Source code hosted in GitHub

Objective:
To automate Docker image builds on every code commit using Azure DevOps pipelines.

