5ï¸âƒ£ CI Pipeline Design Explanation

The CI pipeline was configured using YAML inside Azure DevOps.

Key design decisions:

Trigger on main branch only

Use Microsoft-hosted Ubuntu agent

Separate Docker build tasks for frontend and backend

Modular image naming using variables

Pipeline Tasks:

Pull code from GitHub

Build backend image

Build frontend image

Report build status

No CD implemented in this phase (CI-only implementation).

