Database	MongoDB

7ï¸âƒ£ Design Decisions:

Why Docker?

Environment consistency

Easy portability

Simplified dependency management

Why YAML Pipeline?

Infrastructure as Code

Version-controlled pipeline

Reproducible builds

Why Separate Services?

Loose coupling

Independent scaling (future enhancement)

Better maintainability


